formulas.name: varOpportunityName01
formulas.expression: LEFT( IF( YEAR({!$Record.CloseDate}) >= 2025 && OR( {!$Record.RecordType.Name} = 'Tier2', {!$Record.RecordType.Name} = 'Vision Packages') && !ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.Sales_Type__c} )) && !ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.Opportunity_Product__c})) && !ISBLANK({!$Record.of_Rooftops_for_Opportunity__c}), /*New logic*/ {!$Record.Account.Name} & ' - ' & TEXT({!$Record.Sales_Type__c} ) & ' - ' & TEXT({!$Record.Opportunity_Product__c}) & ' - ' & TEXT({!$Record.of_Rooftops_for_Opportunity__c}) & ' locations', /*old logic*/ {!$Record.Account.Name} &' - '& {!$Record.RecordType.Name} &' - '& TEXT(MONTH({!$Record.CloseDate})) & '/' & TEXT(DAY({!$Record.CloseDate})) & '/' & TEXT(YEAR({!$Record.CloseDate}))) ,120)

formulas.name: varTermRenewal
formulas.expression: CASE({!$Record.Term_Months__c}, '1', '1 Month', '3', '3 Month', '6', '6 Month', '12', '12 Month', NULL)
